il":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (d), the words “notwithstanding any other provisions of law” and “and consolidated with” are omitted as unnecessary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (e), in paragraph (1), the words “Comptroller General” are substituted for “Government Accountability Office” for consistency in the revised title. Paragraph (3) is substituted for “(except in cases where section 1212 of this Appendix is applicable)” because section 1212 applies to all vessels under a construction-differential subsidy contract.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (f), the words “On and after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1956-06-20"},"text":"June 20, 1956","children":[],"tail":"”, and the last proviso in the 4th complete par. at "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/70/319"},"text":"70 Stat. 319","children":[],"tail":" (46 App. U.S.C. 1241b note), are omitted as obsolete."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (g), the words “beginning ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1956-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1956","children":[],"tail":"” and “after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1956-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1956","children":[],"tail":"” are omitted as obsolete."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idf6b87a8b-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idf6b87a8c-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2023—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/118/31"},"text":"Pub. L. 118–31","children":[],"tail":" substituted “("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s4701/a"},"text":"50 U.S.C. 4701(a)","children":[],"tail":", (c), 4703(c), 4704)” for “(50 App. U.S.C. 1291(a), (c), 1293(c), 1294)”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
